    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123430/extras/6fab295685e88720079c1bb7cd59e787.poster.avif?t=1749618814\" width=640 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123430/extras/6fab295685e88720079c1bb7cd59e787.webm?t=1749618814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>BULLCRAP</strong> is a game of lies, poop and deceit!<br><br>Play online with up to <strong>Four</strong> of your friends, with 14 different types of Multiplayer games.<br>Or, play solo over <strong>8 Chapters</strong> of increasingly fun and challenging levels.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Meet <strong>Bucky</strong> the Bull and his untrustworthy farmyard friends!<br></li><li>Call <strong>BULLCRAP!</strong> to punish your friends!<br></li><li>Bend the rules of the game with <strong>Wild Cards</strong>!<br></li><li>Combine Wild Cards to <strong>Power Up</strong>!<br></li><li>Unleash <strong>Chaos</strong> upon the farm!<br></li><li>Things are going to get messy, it’s time to play <strong>Dirty</strong>!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123430/extras/0b3ba01e1e186f04f2b6fabd9b4d84d1.poster.avif?t=1749618814\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123430/extras/0b3ba01e1e186f04f2b6fabd9b4d84d1.webm?t=1749618814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123430/extras/0b3ba01e1e186f04f2b6fabd9b4d84d1.mp4?t=1749618814\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAMEPLAY</h2>The goal of the game is to get rid of <strong>all</strong> of your cards.<br><br>You can do this by <strong>Lying</strong>, or telling the <strong>Truth</strong>!<br>When you think someone is lying, call <strong>&quot;BULLCRAP!&quot;</strong>.<br>If they were lying, they have to pick up <strong>all </strong> the cards.<br>However, if they are telling the truth <strong>you</strong> pick up all the cards.<br><strong>Bluffing</strong> and taking a <strong>Risk</strong> is all part of the fun!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123430/extras/dad3f4037d4a26bff610b988a5e9d164.poster.avif?t=1749618814\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123430/extras/dad3f4037d4a26bff610b988a5e9d164.webm?t=1749618814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123430/extras/dad3f4037d4a26bff610b988a5e9d164.mp4?t=1749618814\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Wild Cards</strong> add an element of chaos to the game, <br>meaning you'll need to switch up your strategy and learn new tricks!<br><br>Inspired by the classic bluff turn-based card game sometimes known as Cheat or Bullsh*t!<br>This is a game for the Deceitful, Courageous and the Bold!",
